{"CLACHAN":[{"def":"A small village containing a church.","pos":""}],"CLACK":[{"def":"To make a sudden, sharp noise, or a succesion of such noises, as by striking an object, or by collision of parts; to rattle; to click.","pos":""},{"def":"To utter words rapidly and continually, or with abruptness; to let the tongue run.","pos":""}],"CLACKER":[{"def":"One who clacks; that which clacks; especially, the clapper of a mill.","pos":""}]}